Class Conditions

java.lang.Object
Conditions
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Conditions
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
Each region (spereated based on plating conditions will have a condition object associated with it The consition object has the soil type, moisture level, sunlight in the region as well as the x,y coordinates of thee outline of that region
